{"tid":2143550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲或者屋企人係識啲香港明星","createTime":"2020-08-07T07:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T13:04:33.000Z","uid":206256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0987609dfec25f82d15990bd025183f0cc10928a","tid":2143550,"uid":206256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"細個聽家母講話佢以前同呀Sa一齊坐過遊艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。家父就話佢同蔡瀾係真frd。但未見過佢地聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲/屋企人係真係識啲香港明星，有contact過或者一齊出席過啲活動。不論係上一代/新一代嘅明星都可以<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54336c3443f44ac941a116472a2e3f4fa6196a2","tid":2143550,"uid":209079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"同人講自己識明星係咪會有優越感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802d71d3180a9cc5bafa90a4439a3286a160e8a8","tid":2143550,"uid":206256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54336c3443f44ac941a116472a2e3f4fa6196a2","tid":2143550,"uid":209079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"同人講自己識明星係咪會有優越感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"完全唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd0b9c7eb13815d4b93a3d24ecc0c226fc84319","tid":2143550,"uid":209079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802d71d3180a9cc5bafa90a4439a3286a160e8a8","tid":2143550,"uid":206256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54336c3443f44ac941a116472a2e3f4fa6196a2","tid":2143550,"uid":209079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"同人講自己識明星係咪會有優越感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"完全唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma